    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个STS系统的控制架构图，核心是ROS 2 Controllers层、Hardware Interface层和实际的Physical Motors三层结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "Hardware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ROS 2 Controllers这层具体包含哪些控制器？我先用subgraph框起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这层有三个：Position Controller、Velocity Controller和Effort Controller，分别对应位置、速度和力矩控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "Position Controller",
        "Velocity Controller",
        "Effort Controller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ROS 2 Controllers子图已经画好，三个控制器节点C1、C2、C3都放进去了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "ROS2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间层是STS Hardware Interface，核心是一个SystemInterface Plugin，它负责把ROS控制器的指令转成硬件信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI",
        "SystemInterface Plugin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "HWI子图已添加，里面放了SI节点标注为SystemInterface Plugin。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最底层是Physical Motors，有三台电机：Motor 1用Position Mode，Motor 2用Velocity Mode，Motor 3比较特殊用PWM Mode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "Motor 1",
        "Motor 2",
        "Motor 3"
